Finally, we'll leave you with our tweet of the week, from journalist Daniel Friebe:

00:07:11.590 --> 00:07:14.620
"A rider whose identity I won't reveal to me recently said:

00:07:14.620 --> 00:07:16.800
'Nibali is meant to be the best descender in the world?

00:07:16.800 --> 00:07:18.080
He's rubbish.

00:07:18.080 --> 00:07:19.819
Rubbish.' "

00:07:19.819 --> 00:07:21.580
Food for thought. What do you think?

00:07:21.580 --> 00:07:22.689
Let us know.

00:07:22.689 --> 00:07:27.630
See you next time.

